---
const blogPosts = [
	{ id: 1, title: 'Why Lead Generation is Key for Business Growth', image: 'image_1.jpg', date: 'Oct. 29, 2019', author: 'Admin', comments: 3 },
	{ id: 2, title: 'Why Lead Generation is Key for Business Growth', image: 'image_2.jpg', date: 'Oct. 29, 2019', author: 'Admin', comments: 3 },
	{ id: 3, title: 'Why Lead Generation is Key for Business Growth', image: 'image_3.jpg', date: 'Oct. 29, 2019', author: 'Admin', comments: 3 },
];
---

<section class="ftco-section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
			{blogPosts.map(post => (
				<div class="col-md-12 text-center d-flex ftco-animate">
					<div class="blog-entry justify-content-end mb-md-5">
						<a href={`/blog/${post.id}`} class="block-20 img" style={`background-image: url('/template-assets/images/${post.image}');`}>
						</a>
						<div class="text px-md-5 pt-4">
							<div class="meta mb-3">
								<div><a href="#">{post.date}</a></div>
								<div><a href="#">{post.author}</a></div>
								<div><a href="#" class="meta-chat"><span class="icon-chat"></span> {post.comments}</a></div>
							</div>
							<h3 class="heading mt-2"><a href={`/blog/${post.id}`}>{post.title}</a></h3>
							<p>A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth.</p>
							<p><a href={`/blog/${post.id}`} class="btn btn-primary">Continue <span class="icon-long-arrow-right"></span></a></p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			))}
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
